Chaninable metrics (preset data)

Config parser

Metric
request url 'http://localhost': 
    fail if cant find string 'Welcome',
    warning if cant find element 'h1',
    warning if cant find elements 'img':
        ???
        warning if cant find attribute 'alt';
    status is 200,
    find link 'a.main-link':
        leads to 'http://localhost'.

    
// Keyword "find" returns collection of objects or sets an error or a warning

for every element - foreach result or context (method addChildLoopAction) 

: passes result to the next metric if it's chainable
, continues on to the next metric with the same result
; closes the cycle and returns to the previous result
. closes the chain or metric

Придется использовать 2 разных HTML парсера. Тогда добавить Interfaces и Contracts
